content.rendered:
Directed by Krishnadev Yagnik. Krishnadev Yagnik.

Cast Ansh Bagri(Vicky). Sarabjeet Bindra(Daljeet aka Dhulla). Vishal Choudhary(Waiter). Sanchay Goswami(Suresh). Nimisha Mehta(Pooja). Anuradha Mukharjee(Isha). Jitendra Pathak(Professor). Hetal Puniwala(Professor). Kinjal Rajpriya(Nisha). Sanket Raval(Puncture guy) . (0)

Language Hindi.

Producers Pratik Choksi. Muffazal Dalal. Zafar Mehdi. Anand Pandit. Aftab Qureshi. Vaishal Shah. Rashmi Sharma. Nishan Singh.

Production Rashmi Sharma Telefilms.
